Package civitas.celestis.object

Class BaseObject

java.lang.Object
civitas.celestis.object.BaseObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
Movable, Physical, Renderable, Unique
public class BaseObject extends Object implements Unique, Movable, Physical, Renderable

BaseObject

The base implementation of an object that is unique, movable, has physical properties, and can be rendered.
